title: Piz Ajüz
text: Piz Ajüz (2,788 m) is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> in the <a href="Sesvenna%20Range">Sesvenna Range</a> of the <a href="Alps">Alps</a>, located south-east of <a href="Scuol">Scuol</a> in the canton of <a href="Graub%C3%BCnden">Graubünden</a>. It lies north of <a href="Piz%20Triazza">Piz Triazza</a>, on the range between the Val Triazza and the Val d'Uina.
